#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is the user manual for &kphotoalbum;. If you are not the type who "
#| "likes reading documentation, but rather just want to try out things, here "
#| "are a few alternatives:"
msgid ""
"This is the user manual for &kphotoalbum; &mdash; a digital image "
"cataloguing software that supports annotation, browsing, searching and "
"viewing of digital images and videos. If you are not the type who likes "
"reading documentation, but rather just want to try out things, here are a "
"few alternatives:"
msgstr ""
"Este é o manual do usuario do &kphotoalbum;. Se non é dos que lles gusta ler "
"a documentación e prefire experimentar coas cousas, velaquí ten algunhas "
"alternativas:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Homepage</"
"ulink>, and look at the quick overview, screen shoots, and introduction "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"Vaia á <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">páxina web de &kphotoalbum;"
"</ulink> e mire a presentación rápida, as capturas de pantalla e os vídeos "
"introdutorios."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Start &kphotoalbum;, and accepts its offer for a demo (If this is your "
#| "first time you start it), or go to <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu and "
#| "select <guimenuitem>Run &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. That will load "
#| "&kphotoalbum; with a number of images, and let you browse around."
msgid ""
"Start &kphotoalbum;, and accept its offer for a demo (If this is your first "
"time you start it), or go to <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu and select "
"<guimenuitem>Run &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. That will load "
"&kphotoalbum; with a number of images, and let you browse around."
msgstr ""
"Inicie o &kphotoalbum; e accepte a súa oferta de demostración (se é a "
"primeira vez que o inicia) ou vaia ao menú <guimenu>Axuda</guimenu> e "
"escolla <guimenuitem>Executar a demostración do &kphotoalbum;</guimenuitem>. "
"Con isto arranca o &kphotoalbum; con varias imaxes, co que pode ver como vai."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you prefer to print out this document, then you may find it as on long "
#| "HTML document at <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/"
#| "\">&kphotoalbum;'s Homepage</ulink>"
msgid ""
"If you prefer to print out this document, then you may find it as on long "
"PDF document at <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink>. A "
"direct link is available at <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index.php?"
"page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum;'s Homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Se prefire imprimir este documento, pódeo atopar como documento longo en "
"HTML na <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">páxina web do "
"&kphotoalbum;</ulink>"

